import React from "react"
import { Image, Title, Article, Body } from "../styles/card"

// eslint-disable-next-line react/prop-types
const Card = ({ source, title, article }) => (
  <>
    <Body>
      <Image src={source} alt="icon" />
      <Title>{title}</Title>
      <Article>{article}</Article>
    </Body>
  </>
)

export default Card
